{"tid":1285554,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屯門公園嘅「光復行動」應該分兩日進行","createTime":"2019-07-04T15:26:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T16:57:23.000Z","uid":134134,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c89a41642040f33cdf988d87e6d498f9bb2fa19a","tid":1285554,"uid":134134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T15:26:59.000Z","msg":"喺啲藍絲專頁度見到，唔少藍絲中年人同老人其實都好支持今次嘅光復行動。正如<span style=\"color: teal;\">orion1</span>巴打所言，其實喺無關政黨立場嘅民生議題上，呢班中老年人一樣深受赤化所害，所以呢班中老年人立場上同我哋應該會係大同小異架喎。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n伸延閱讀：<br />\n與藍絲結盟！！「政治放兩旁、藍黃為香港」聯盟正式成立！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1285196\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1285196</a><br />\n<br />\n咁點解去到討論解決一啲民生以至法制問題上面，唔同年齡、背景嘅人會出出現咁大嘅分歧呢 ？ 我認為除咗因為長時間受政黨分化，同資訊接收圈子內嘅回音效應影響外，對<span style=\"color: gold;\">有效抗爭</span>嘅理解截然不同都係一個好重要嘅原因。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">一啲人認為，抗爭一定要守法，跟政府安排提出反對意見；而明眼人就知，如果政府一意孤行或者愛理不理，呢啲方法根本唔撚work。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n咁我哋應該點樣教佢哋呢個大道理呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今次呢個光復行動就係一個好機會啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我哋要將今次行動分兩日進行：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">第一日：和平理性非暴力</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我哋剩要過去<span style=\"color: green;\">好言相勸</span>啲大陸雞，叫佢哋好好做人，唔好再喺度賣藝。俾班雞鬧關你咩事嘅時候就即刻<span style=\"color: green;\">敗走</span>。亦都唔搞佢哋啲音響器材，唔阻止阿伯入去跳舞捐錢。得閒<span style=\"color: green;\">派下傳單</span>叫人注意屯門公園噪音問題。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">實行不阻止、不打擾、不拆檔，最好唱埋今天我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n如無意外，跟住落嚟一個星期，班雞同雞蟲應該馬照跑錢照收。文宣組呢個時候就要出動，將和平光復完之後嘅情況如實宣揚開去。令到班阿嬸諗：搞錯呀，咁多人阻止過，反對過都仲係咁嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">第二日：嚟料啦，勇武！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n同第一日完全相反，誓要將全部檔口<span style=\"color: red;\">趕盡殺絕！</span>追住啲雞嚟鬧，圍住啲雞嚟鬧，鬧住鬧完再鬧，<span style=\"color: red;\">鬧到佢哋唔敢再嚟為止</span>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當然我絕對唔鼓勵人<span style=\"color: red;\">拆檔，將佢哋嘅音響破壞氹落水，或者將佢哋啲錢兜踢走，甚至傷害到佢哋身體嘅行為 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n唔使擔心佢哋一嚟就報警，因為唔知點解啲新移民總有一種對警察嘅恐懼感。而且佢哋都無嗰種俾人侵害要搵人幫手，要反抗嘅價值觀。<br />\n<br />\n如無意外，屯門公園跟住都至少都會有幾日安寧。咁班中老年人就見識到有時有啲嘢，<span style=\"color: gold;\">喺無賴面前真係勇武先有用。</span><br />\n<br />\n而之後嘅屯門公園，過幾個禮拜之後又會故態復萌，到時又有賴各位重複住光復行動。<br />\n<br />\n呢個係一個長期抗爭，而且尖沙咀土瓜灣等地方都有同樣問題。讓我等待住各位遍地開花。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d6bdf2adb413d2ab9c82f56dc17dd27fc949f9b","tid":1285554,"uid":200758,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T15:28:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OJfWtfJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOJfWtfJ.jpg&h=3b2d02f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r6QrQt4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr6QrQt4.jpg&h=02ad2ebb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wF8MOUk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwF8MOUk.png&h=6fe51bde&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"034b71de88ed3a17b801e5844a9316bb98766e5d","tid":1285554,"uid":45830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T15:33:14.000Z","msg":"每日幾次添啦"},{"pid":"b30e9e6e031946e5a8aefe789284df1144204ffe","tid":1285554,"uid":49151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T16:08:23.000Z","msg":"呢個要keep住搞"},{"pid":"527468012fa2bfb4db14d8087099af4a3a056842","tid":1285554,"uid":134134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"034b71de88ed3a17b801e5844a9316bb98766e5d","tid":1285554,"uid":45830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T15:33:14.000Z","msg":"每日幾次添啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T16:11:24.000Z","msg":"人數都唔同，點可以比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f8362ec4e8dcb394729279558a7ca91e60a2eee","tid":1285554,"uid":82640,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T16:54:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/O3HNAp9.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO3HNAp9.gif&h=9cee48d5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7b75a35544a9119ed6e08b94117563eab40e9bf4","tid":1285554,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f8362ec4e8dcb394729279558a7ca91e60a2eee","tid":1285554,"uid":82640,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T16:54:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/O3HNAp9.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO3HNAp9.gif&h=9cee48d5&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T16:55:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfb5ef07491311a8da35d16d621ad2aabc6f181f","tid":1285554,"uid":142770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T16:57:23.000Z","msg":"佢地兩點鐘有開檔架啦 <br />\n有時仲有啲阿伯開咪唱歌 極難聽極騷擾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}